summary: These files are destined to be used for generating LOD for Skyrim Original Edition in the Creation Kit.
descriptionHtml:
[color=#a4c2f4][size=4][b]Important:[/b][/size][/color]

If you use these files to generate the LOD for Skyrim Special Edition, you must make them with the Creation Kit that goes with Skyrim Original Edition. Making them with the Creation Kit that comes with Skyrim Special Edition will not work.

The related tutorial is here:

[center][color=#a4c2f4][size=4][b][u][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/articles/51294]How to generate Level of Detail (LOD) for a custom world space[/url]﻿[/u]﻿[/b][/size][/color][/center]

[color=#a4c2f4][size=4][b]Note:[/b][/size][/color]

I have extracted these files myself from my Skyrim 1.9.32 install, after studying the corresponding files Nico coiN uploaded to AFK Mods.

[center]-----oOo-----[/center]
[color=#a4c2f4][size=3][b]Please, do not forget to credit this tutorial and myself when you use it for one of your mod and provide a link to this place. Thank you![/b][/size][/color]
author: anneschmidt
